burlap.behavior.singleagent.planning.vfa.fittedvi

Class WekaVFATrainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.planning.vfa.fittedvi.WekaVFATrainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SupervisedVFA

    public class WekaVFATrainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements SupervisedVFA
    A class for using supervised learning algorithms provided by the Weka library for fitted value iteration. This class takes a generator for Weka Classifier objects (specified with the WekaVFATrainer.WekaClassifierGenerator interface and a StateToFeatureVectorGenerator to turn BURLAP State objects into feature vectors usable by Weka.

    This class also provides the static method getKNNTrainer(burlap.behavior.singleagent.vfa.StateToFeatureVectorGenerator, int) for construction of the Weka instance-based regression algorithm IBk, since instance-based methods have convergence guarantees for fitted value iteration.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
